- Extensions
  - Pin to Toolbar: Simple Tab Groups, 1Password
- Customize Toolbar..., 
	- Account, Pin to Overflow Menu
	- (left) Home, Sidebars
	- (right) Simple Tab Groups, 1Password, Downloads Extensions
	- (overflow) Firefox Account
	- Toolbars, Bookmarks Toolbar, Never Show
- 1Password, Settings, General
	- Watchtower, check Check for vulnerable passwords
	- Notifications, Watchtower alerts
- Bookmarks search plus 2, Options 
  - Search results bookmark behaviour=Advanced click
	- uncheck Match active FF theme, check Override text color to white and background color to black"
}

